query:
SELECT sk.id, sk.keyword, COUNT(dq.id) as query_count 
FROM seedKeywords sk 
LEFT JOIN derivativeQueries dq ON sk.id = dq.seedKeywordId 
WHERE sk.projectId = (SELECT projectId FROM analysisSessions WHERE id = 1)
GROUP BY sk.id, sk.keyword;
